: : Heartbreak : :

The transwarp portal opens as a small one bot Cybertronion transport comes through. It is heading directly towards Earth.

Inside the ship one Transformer sits, piloting the ship. He is obviously a flight model, and looks to be quite armed.

Heartbreak: I actually made it, thank Primus. I though the Trpredacus were going to kill me. I still cant believe that they have taken over Cybertron. I barely escaped. I better set this thing down.

The ship heads down into the atmosphere.


Heartbreak: Too bad I had to leave the Kliq behind... not to mention all those cute femmes.

We can tell by his voice that he is a young bot. If he was humna he would seem to be about 16 or 17 years of age.

The ship land in what will eventually be San Antonio, Texas, USA.

Heartbreak steps out of the ship and looks around.

Heartbreak: Neo Beast Wars, the icon, the show stopper, the main event, IS HERE!

Heartbreak transformes to his jet mode and flies off in the eastern direction.

--Boundary_(ID_PbG7UusY4cnEA6ubVyNaRw)
